{"article_id":"kQiJp6soHQeXm5d8","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Washington ( CNN ) -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"House Speaker John Boehner said","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"he 's `` not confident at all ''","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"that Congress can reach a budget deal","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"to avert the so-called `` fiscal cliff '' at the end of this year .","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"On Tuesday morning","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"Moody 's , a credit rating agency , released a report","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"threatening to lower the U.S. government 's AAA credit rating","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"if Congress did n't agree to a major deficit reduction package .","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"Asked by CNN","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"how confident he was","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"that congressional negotiators could avoid that action","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"Boehner replied ,","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"`` I 'm not confident at all . '' -","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"Check out the CNN Electoral Map and Calculator","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"and game out your own strategy for November .","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"The fiscal cliff is the combination of the automatic cuts to federal programs","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"scheduled to go into effect in January","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"and the tax increases","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"that would result from expiration of all of the `` Bush era '' tax cuts at the end of this year .","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"The speaker maintained","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"that House Republicans already passed legislation","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"to replace those spending cuts","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"and extend all the current tax rates .","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"`` Listen the House has done its job on both the sequester and the looming tax hikes","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"that will cost our economy some 700,000 jobs , ''","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"Boehner said ,","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"and shifted the blame to Democrats ,","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"adding ,","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"`` The Senate at some point has to act .","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"And on both of these - where is the President ?","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"Where 's the leadership ?","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"Absent","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"without leading . ''","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"Although Moody 's report specified","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"it would consider cutting the government 's rating","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"if an agreement did n't emerge in the next year ,","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"an aide to Boehner told CNN","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"that the speaker 's comments reflected his confidence level","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"about reaching a deal by the end of 2012 .","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"Without any serious bipartisan negotiations taking place ,","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"both parties are expected to return to the issue in the lame duck session of Congress in mid-November .","depth":6},{"id":42,"text":"House Democratic Whip Steny Hoyer , D-Maryland , said","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"there were some discussions going on now ,","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"but conceded","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"`` there has not been a great deal of movement ' on any potential budget deal .","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"But Hoyer was more upbeat about a deal","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"emerging -","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"after the election .","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"`` I am optimistic","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"that","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"once this election is over","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"that the patriotism of members","depth":14},{"id":53,"text":"- Republicans and Democrats -","depth":14},{"id":54,"text":"will come","depth":13},{"id":55,"text":"and summon them to coming to an agreement on the most important question","depth":14},{"id":56,"text":"confronting this nation","depth":14},{"id":57,"text":"and that is putting this nation on a more fiscally sustainable credible path . ''","depth":13},{"id":58,"text":"Even after Congress reached a deal in the summer of 2011","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"to raise the debt limit","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"and agreed to a series of spending cuts ,","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"Standard & Poor 's , one of Moody 's rival credit rating agencies , downgraded for the first time the U.S. credit rating .","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"As part of the automatic cuts , the military would especially be hit hard","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"--a measure","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"both parties say","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"they want to prevent .","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"A spokeswoman for President Barack Obama 's re-election campaign said","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"the president `` agrees","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"that we should avoid the automatic defense cuts . ''","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"`` That 's why he has called on Congressional Republicans to help prevent them with a balanced plan","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"that asks millionaires and billionaires to pay their fair share , ''","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"Lis Smith said in a statement .","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"The president 's plan has some support in the Democratic-controlled Senate .","depth":5},{"id":73,"text":"Responding to Boehner 's comments ,","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"Senate Majority Leader Harry Reid said","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"he was `` disappointed . ''","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"`` I think","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"we have to look at the glass being half-full ,","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"not half-empty all the time .","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"I 'm confident","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"we will reach some kind of an arrangement , ''","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"Reid told reporters on Capitol Hill .","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"`` We will continue with the middle class tax cut","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"that the Senate passed .","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"It 's much , much too early","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"to give up . ''","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"Asked what made him so optimistic about a deal ,","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"Reid pointed to what he sees as dwindling momentum for the tea party .","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"`` I 've been here for a while ,","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"and I believe","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"once the elections are over ,","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"the tea party strength will be significantly weakened , ''","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"On her part , House Democratic Leader Nancy Pelosi released a statement ,","depth":4},{"id":94,"text":"calling on Boehner to keep the chamber in session","depth":5},{"id":95,"text":"until they solve the problem .","depth":5},{"id":96,"text":"`` Democrats are committed to staying in session","depth":6},{"id":97,"text":"as long as it takes","depth":7},{"id":98,"text":"to ensure certainty for the middle class and growth for the economy , ''","depth":7},{"id":99,"text":"she said .","depth":5},{"id":100,"text":"`` The ball is in Speaker Boehner 's court . ''","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":201,"left":0,"right":200,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":200,"left":192,"right":199,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":192,"left":139,"right":191,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":139,"left":115,"right":138,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":115,"left":113,"right":114,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":113,"left":104,"right":112,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":104,"left":1,"right":103,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":103,"left":2,"right":102,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":102,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":112,"left":107,"right":111,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":107